snippet.textDisplay: Pehli bat tu ye k shikwa ko gane k leay bhot ehtiat krni chaheay thi jo nae ki gae. kahi tu bhot acha sur laga lekin jahan sur na laga wahan asan jaga lene ki bajae in mohtarma ne chekh k dharh k Har akhir mushkil misre ko jharh pila di. baki qawwal hazrat ka piece us se b zeada betartibi or Shor sharabe ka shikar hy. Isi music ko kisi b or Shair k gane me adjust kr lete tou thik tha. Allama iqbal ki shairi k sath is qadar be saliqa Cher char muje tu kam az kam bilkul achi nae lagi. Jin logo ko samaj araha hy wo ya tu mehez mukhtalif awazon or gaiki ka tal Mel dekh rey hn ya pir music ka acha arrangement haqiqat pasandi ki nigah se dekhen iqbal ki shairi ki esi durgat banne pe apka dil khoon k ansoo roega.
